# OUROBOROS Mutations Log

> Record of all system mutations

## Format

```json
{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-14T16:00:00Z",
  "mutation_id": "mut_001",
  "type": "A|B|C",
  "description": "What changed",
  "trigger": "What caused it",
  "approval": "auto|user|pending",
  "status": "active|rolled_back|validated",
  "impact": "measured_effect"
}
```
